=== EVENT_TIME_DISTORTION ===
# id: 29
# title: Time Distortion
# chinese_title: 时间扭曲
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

Clocks begin running backwards. Crew members report seeing echoes of themselves from minutes ago. Something is very wrong with local spacetime.

* [Investigate the source]
  ~ gain_radical("时")
  时间 (shíjiān) — time
* [Reverse engines and retreat] {requires: fuel >= 4}
  ~ lose_fuel(4)
  撤退 (chètuì) — retreat
* [Shut down all systems and drift through]
  ~ damage_crew(5)
  关闭 (guānbì) — shut down
